sequenceDiagram
  participant User as User
  participant UI as cosmo-browse-ui
  participant IPC as Tauri IPC
  participant Session as Orbit Session
  participant Net as Loader/Network
  participant Parse as DOM/Frameset Parser
  participant Render as Render Pipeline

  User->>UI: URL入力 / ナビゲーション操作
  UI->>IPC: open_url / activate_link
  IPC->>Session: execute_navigation
  Session->>Net: fetch_document
  Net-->>Session: HTML bytes + metadata
  Session->>Parse: decode_html + parse_document
  Parse-->>Session: Frame tree / DOM model
  Session->>Render: build page snapshot
  Render-->>UI: GalaxyFrame + scene_items
  UI-->>User: 初回描画

  User->>UI: click / key event
  UI->>IPC: activate_link / dispatch event
  IPC->>Session: event handling + state update
  Session->>Render: relayout / repaint
  Render-->>UI: updated snapshot
  UI-->>User: 再描画
